raw_text = "~ start
do Story.set_location(\"mabels_room\")
Mabel: Babe!
Mabel: Emergency!!
Player: Huh what?
Player: What's going on??
Mabel: I CAN'T DECIDE WHAT TO WEAR TODAY!!
if Story.mabel_trust < 50:
	Player: Oh no, here we go again 😆
	Mabel: Baaaabe this isn't funny 🥹
	Player: Don't worry, I wasn't expecting to get through college without one of your closet crises	
	Mabel: I'll try not to take hours this time since we have class 😇
	Player: We'll see about that 😂
	Mabel: 🙄
	Mabel: So you'll help? 🥹
	Player: Sure why not 😄
else:
	Player: Another closet crisis?
	Mabel: Am I annoying you?
	Player: Not at all!
	Player: It's a little nostalgic honestly
	Mabel: R-really? 🥺❤️
	Player: Mhmm, I like helping you with it
	Player: And I get some cute pictures!
	Mabel: I'll send you a million cute pics right now if you want 😭
	Mabel: You're so sweet
Mabel: Ok ok so!
Mabel: Mom packed me some new clothes and...
Mabel: Honestly I don't know what she was thinking 😅
Mabel: I haven't touched them yet but I don't wanna wear the same thing every day y'know 😊
Mabel: All the other girls are working on their styles so I have to look pretty!!
Player: Mhmm
Mabel: Baaaabe
Mabel: Don't you want people to know you have the prettiest girl ever 🥰
- Definitely! [#lust]
	set Story.mabel_desire += 1
	Player: Definitely!
	Mabel: Oh okay
	Mabel: That was fast 😳
	Mabel: Thought: I don't know what you're thinking babe but it better not be something naughty!
- I want it to be my secret! [#love]
	set Story.mabel_desire -= 1
	Player: I want it to be my secret
	Mabel: Awwh baaabe 😭
	Mabel: It'll be for you then 🥰
	Player: Perfect 😘
Mabel: Okay okay, photoshoot time!
if Story.mabel_desire <= 0:
	Mabel: I like this one
	Mabel: img: mabel/43
	Mabel: It reminds me of one of my dresses I had to throw away cause I got taller hehe
	Mabel: So cute!
	Player: VERY!
	Mabel: Even now, so far away from home, I feel like Mom is still thinking of me 🥰
	Player: That's true, I'm sure she is
Mabel: What do you think of this one?
Mabel: img: mabel/45
Mabel: It's a bit similar to the one I went out with Nina
Mabel: I think I'm a little more comfortable in it
Mabel: It's what all the other girls like to wear
Mabel: I guess dresses aren't so popular here 🤭
Player: I haven't seen many girls in dresses either
if Story.mabel_desire > 0:
	Mabel: Okay don't laugh but there's also this..
	Mabel: img: mabel/47
	Mabel: I kind of hid this from Nina when she came over because I thought... y'know 😇
	Mabel: I wasn't ready to wear something like this
	Mabel: I think it's probably not as bad as I thought though
	Mabel: Look a little \"hot\" ☺️
	Mabel: Only because you like it, right??
	Player: Wow this is, different
	Mabel: Okay don't stare too hard 😵‍💫 It was just a test 😇
Mabel: Well? What do you think? 🥰
- The dress is super pretty [#love] [if Story.mabel_desire <= 0]
	set Story.mabel_desire -= 1
	Player: The dress is super pretty!
	set Story.flag = \"CuteOutfit\"
	Mabel: Omg you think so?
	Mabel: PinkThought: Here I was thinking that my style was getting boring but you're here to prove me wrong
	Mabel: 🥰
	Player: Yeah of course!
	Player: Why the reaction? haha 😆
	Mabel: Ooh just girl thoughts hehe 😊
- The sweater and tee are a perfect balance [#trust]
	set Story.mabel_trust += 1
	Player: The sweater and tee are a perfect balance
	set Story.flag = \"ModernOutfit\"
	Mabel: Omg I was thinking the exact same thing!!
	Mabel: I guess I'm not so much a small town girl anymore
	Mabel: It's better to fit in a little more
	Mabel: I think I'll still keep my dresses for some special occassions
	Mabel: But it might be better to wear something like this instead of my old sweater collection 😅
	Player: Sounds good!
- Second one is way too hot to not wear [#lust] [if Story.mabel_desire > 0]
	set Story.mabel_desire += 1
	Player: Second one is way too hot to not wear
	set Story.flag = \"HotOutfit\"
	Mabel: At first I thought my mom bought the wrong size but then when I saw girls wearing this on the first day 😳
	Mabel: Mom knew what she was doing 😅
	Mabel: I guess she's been through it too and just wanted me to have more choices 🥹
	Player: 😁
	Mabel: Well at least you're enjoying it 🥹😂
Mabel: Alright, all dressed up now
Mabel: I feel kind of like a new me!
Mabel: Even though it's the same old Mabel 😆
Player: I'm happy it's working out!
Mabel: It is I guess 🥰
Mabel: Gotta run now!
if Story.mabel_desire <= 0:
	Mabel: Love you!! 😘
	Player: Love you too ❤️
do social_post(\"caleb_hometown\")
=> END"
metadata/dialogue_manager_version = "3.7.1"
